Enum Constant Detail

Finished

public static final WorkItem.State Finished
The work item was finished normally. For work items of type Approval, this indicates approval.

Rejected

public static final WorkItem.State Rejected
The work item was rejected. Currently used only with Approval work items.

Returned

public static final WorkItem.State Returned
The owner decided not to accept this work item. Note that this is semantically different than "reject" in an Approval item. It means that no action was taken or that the user had no opinion.

Expired

public static final WorkItem.State Expired
The work item expired with no action taken.

Pending

public static final WorkItem.State Pending
When an approval workitem is first created it will start in the pending state

Canceled

public static final WorkItem.State Canceled
The work item was canceled with no user input. This state should only be set by the workflow engine.
